  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I have a tendency also to stutter when I-- when I get nervous.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was about 1938 or '39, I can't recall exactly, but it was-- was very close to-- between '39, so a year before the war [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't recall that either, because they were-- they must have-- they must have taken them out, they must have-- maybe the parents-- I don't remember that, no.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I know they were children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were different kind of children there of different-- especially Germany, there were-- when they were chased out from Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, not preoccupied-- I used to like to go to-- to the orphanages and feel like-- I didn't do it continuously, but I used to like to go to the orphanages [INAUDIBLE] to the [INAUDIBLE] old people.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I used to-- I used to feel, for some reason, probably the closest there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I felt like a-- a compassion for these people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably beginning of '39, when I--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was beginning to feel that I am involved as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'm involved in the situation myself, [INAUDIBLE] because I'm beginning-- I was 14 years old already, going to be 14-- I-- I became to be 14 years old, no.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my-- the talk was going around, the way people were talking on the radio, no.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw-- I saw people talking about it, no, that-- that something is going on in Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were showing pictures of Hitler [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were showing they way he was expressing his [? word, ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the way he was teaching his people how to hurt other people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I saw the kristall-- I saw the-- when they were breaking windows.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
